        <h1> Let´s visit whales!</h1>
        <h2> A brief introduction</h2>
        <p>Hello! I´m from Colombia and I want to tell about a great plan to do if you visit this country. 
            I'm talking about see the amazing, and pretty beautiful humpback whales in the pacific ocean. </p>

        <figure>
            <img src="project/buenaventura.jpeg" 
            width="50%"  alt="Sculpture of a whale in Buenaventura's pier ">
        </figure>

        <p>If you want to know what can you do there, let me give you some ideas:</p>
        <h2> To do list</h2>
                <ul>
                <li> Swim in the beach</li>
                <li> Eat delicious sea food</li>
                <li> Visit the local fair</li> 
                <li> Do trekking and see waterfalls</li> 
                <li><strong> Of course, admire humpback whales </strong></li>  
            </ul>
        <hr>           

        <p>When I went there, I traveled during a weekend with a vey nice agency trip, call <strong>Xperiencia.</strong>
            On the itinerary, they included many local activities, two whale sightings and a lot of boat rides.
            It was amazing!</p>
        <hr>

